des:
This skill contains surprising things you didn’t know about Zagreb, Croatia and it's people. Croatia and it's Capital is the latest trendy destination among tourists worldwide, so this is an ideal skill to find out why. 
Download Zagreb Facts on you Alexa and find out the things you didn’t know about Zagreb – and why you might want to add it to your itinerary.
